    <title>What the student sees</title>
    <para>onCourse has a password free purchasing process meaning that students don't have to
        remember obsure student identification details from their last enrolment. Where a student
        has enrolled previously they can move immediately to the payment process, automatically
        matched to their previous record.</para>
